    <h2>Method</h2>

    <ol>
        <li>In a casserole dish, heat some olive oil with the parmesan rind.</li>
        <li>Add the chicken pieces and brown on all sides.</li>
        <li>Add the cashews, pine nuts, prunes and bay leaves, then add the wine and stock to cover most of the chicken.</li>
        <li>Cover the pot, and cook on a low heat for 1 hour.</li>
        <li>Serve with rice or mashed potato and garnish with a few pine nuts.</li>
    </ol>

